@startuml
title UC7 Easy Sequence - Provide Feedback
autonumber
hide footbox

actor User
boundary UI
control FeedbackCtrl
entity FeedbackStore
entity Cache

User -> UI : vote(answerId, approve/disapprove)
UI -> FeedbackCtrl : submitVote(answerId, vote)

FeedbackCtrl -> FeedbackStore : save(vote)
alt approve
  FeedbackCtrl -> Cache : keep/prioritize(answerId)
else disapprove
  FeedbackCtrl -> Cache : invalidate(answerId)
end

FeedbackCtrl --> UI : ack()
UI --> User : confirmation
@enduml